Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:10.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:38.34,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,With the guidance of the ten elves \Nknown as the Apostles of Sephira,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:42.39,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the border between this world and \Nthe next that lay inside Clover Castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:44.77,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Shadow Palace, appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:48.54,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,When we put the final magic stone \Nin its pedestal inside the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:51.73,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,the elves' reincarnation \Nwill be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:55.18,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, the souls of the \Nhumans who owned these bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:58.99,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,will be sent to the underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:02.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, there's a magical \Nspace spreading over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:05.98,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why don't we head on over?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:12.30,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We will not let you get in the \Nway of the Apostles of Sephira!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:16.26,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,It's just one thing after another... \NGive us a break already, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.85,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who arrived during \Nthis time of crisis were...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:22.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.89,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:27.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:31.90,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,A stupidly huge... bull?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:35.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of entrance was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:37.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, you dumbasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:41.11,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, humans! It doesn't \Nmatter how many of you show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.16,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,You're no match for us elves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:48.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It looked as though the tables had turned \Nthanks to Asta and the others, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:52.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. Don't tell me this ki is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:54.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:58.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the Coral Peacocks,\N Dorothy Unsworth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:03.18,main,Reve,0000,0000,0000,,Dream Magic: Glamour World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:06.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Dorothy Unsworth,\N the Captain of the Coral Peacocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:09.06,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,had also reincarnated as an elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:12.75,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,She used her magic to teleport Vanessa \Nand the others into the dream world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.69,Ep Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,The Eyes in the Mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.55,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La! La!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:51.93,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.13,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see too well without my glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.67,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:58.66,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this weird place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:02.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the magic of the \NCaptain of the Coral Peacocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:07.93,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge wasn't able to evade it because \Nshe couldn't identify it as an attack spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.15,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:14.78,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is one of the most \Npowerful spells a single mage can produce!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.19,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to be so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.85,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This place goes on forever. \NI don't think there's an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:26.11,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Like that's even possible,\N Luck, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.93,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably more possible \Nthan you ever not being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.95,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The hell did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:37.63,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,Making the impossible possible is \Nwhat happens here in the Glamour World.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:41.88,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:45.63,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,to the world where I control everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.68,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The bed just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.23,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.69,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,is as I wish it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.94,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-S-Some kind of strange \Ncreature just appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:00.48,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,And it just keeps getting bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.53,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:05.03,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,So you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.53,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,absolutely no chance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.83,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:17.33,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,You can sleep forever now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.34,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,How dare it try to eat us instead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:30.09,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we died, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.73,italics,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,The result changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:39.10,italics,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,So that magic really does \Nhave to do with logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:43.18,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,That cat really is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.06,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not one of the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:49.23,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If you stray too far, her magic \Nwon't affect you, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:51.81,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So it just works on your teammates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:54.24,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there'd have to be \Nlimits on a spell this amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:57.62,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Dream magic and thread magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.22,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,These two witches are absolutely amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.79,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna research them so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.22,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I think she's bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.17,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:13.73,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Once you've used magic,\Neat up so you can recover mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:17.06,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,That magic's amazing, too! \NYou're not a witch, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.06,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I just like to eat lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:24.06,italics,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,An inexhaustible magic supply \Nand absolute evasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.78,italics,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,This is not going to be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:30.28,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If this ridiculous place is magic, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,then we can get outta here if we beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.45,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.08,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,Useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.25,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she can use any magical attribute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.94,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what her limits even are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.37,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.43,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell cares?! This isn't fun at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:58.10,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, what are we even supposed \Nto do? She's basically invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.69,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic's not that interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.61,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The hell did you just say?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.27,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.81,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.28,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.67,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the cornerstone of our defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:15.03,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,and Charmy's vital to mana recovery.\NWe can't both stay stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:17.79,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry back to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:20.29,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.47,0:07:30.13,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is make sure we \Nevade with Rouge's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:32.30,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time to recover your mana, la.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.30,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Eat, eat, eat, Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.72,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray, hooray, Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.02,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, appetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.64,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to slap all of you\Nif I get fat from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:46.97,italics,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be some kind of \Nlimit to her healing abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.46,italics,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,An ever-flowing pool of water
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.77,italics,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,that happens to have blade-fish \Nperpetually spawning from it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.59,italics,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,A never-ending barrage of attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:02.59,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,My noms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:03.71,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.63,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Water, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:09.38,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Say, lightning boy, could you \Nattack that pool of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.21,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can destroy \Nsomething that big, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:14.13,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. Just give it your all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.68,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Magic: Thunderbolt Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:24.01,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, it didn't work after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:26.62,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now you attack, fire protozoan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:29.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling a fire \Nprotozoan, you dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:32.49,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just shoot it with \Neverything you've got already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.90,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:41.87,italics,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,If I guessed correctly and \Nthat really is water...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.78,italics,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,It'll explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:53.91,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Look at that intensity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:55.71,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:59.26,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,I used electricity to chemically decompose \Nwater, then set fire to what was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.10,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:04.34,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, if you unleash lightning \Nmagic and flame magic on water,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:07.48,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,you can create an explosion big \Nenough to destroy a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:11.27,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What were you thinking, \Nmaking us do something that dangerous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.24,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? You can use the cat to evade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.24,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try this with Noelle's magic next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:21.02,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,That experiment made a \Nfew other things clear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:25.29,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,First, what she's generating are \Nactual objects she visualized.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.87,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,That means real-world \Nprinciples work on them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.67,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Nom! This is a real fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:34.88,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Second, because of that, \Nshe can't manipulate
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:38.18,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,the spells we cast and the resulting phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.90,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. Otherwise, that explosion and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:45.14,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge's ability to manipulate \Nfate wouldn't have worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.67,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:52.15,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Third, it's still going to \Nbe really hard to beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:58.53,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry up and find a way outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.83,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have that kind of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.95,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Charmy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.21,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm so sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:10.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:13.33,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't no time for... sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.54,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.72,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:23.72,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you couldn't evade the drowsiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:29.67,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that exists in Glamour World \Nwill eventually get drowsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:34.35,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,And those who fall asleep \Nwill never awaken again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:37.14,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:42.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to stay awake even during \Nall of Mister Yami's all-nighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.54,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. At this rate... \NBut I don't know what we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:54.04,main,Dorothy,0000,0000,0000,,Sink slowly into the sleep of death, \Nunable to do anything within this space.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:11:00.05,italics,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, everything that was already \Nblurry is getting even blurrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.65,italics,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Not having my glasses seriously sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.14,italics,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:05.42,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:11.02,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what these are? The answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.73,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:16.44,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what the hell are you talking about?\N Now's not the time for—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.94,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.38,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:23.79,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:26.38,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in this world \Nhappens as she sees fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:30.00,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,So things that she visualized \Nin her head appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.62,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:38.59,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,What this world needs... is an \Nexit, exit, exit! Make one, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:50.83,main,Sally,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to not think of something once \Nyour mind has already visualized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:55.15,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah! She's only \Ninvincible in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:57.94,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,If we can escape it,\Nwe can figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We keep seeing the same \Nstuff no matter how far we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.62,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even find any walls, let alone Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:23.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And this faint ki I feel... Is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:28.82,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like someone's \Nmagic is making us get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:34.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you noticed it, \Ntoo, you beanpole weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.71,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you, meathead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:42.69,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,They've got some nerve hiding.\NI wanna slash them up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:43.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.49,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm gonna slash them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I found them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:50.74,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I was first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:51.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:52.76,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, you're such a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.71,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,The early bird slashes the worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.21,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,You're right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:05.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you slashing? \NThe enemy's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:08.96,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,What?! They're right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:12.27,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you didn't even hit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, neither did you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:18.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, whatever! I'm done with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:20.81,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line, you stupid meathead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.88,main,Jack,0000,0000,0000,,You useless beanpole!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.53,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:29.11,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Though they were technically both \Ncorrect in my warped space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:33.51,main,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness I rolled a six \Nin order to keep them busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:37.14,italics,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,The higher the number with dice magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:40.04,italics,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,the more effective it is \Nin the situation at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:43.63,italics,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone get in the way \Nof the Apostles of Sephira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.14,italics,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,I would appreciate it if
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:48.59,italics,Baval,0000,0000,0000,,these two would keep quiet\N for just a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.69,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I can't keep this up anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:04.40,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Their overall magic power \Nis way higher than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:12.53,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I... am... going... to... \Nreach... my... limit... soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.41,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Why not give up already, humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.33,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.84,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:30.09,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get into my black form...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:33.14,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't even have a chance to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:38.14,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.40,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that all we can do is watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.66,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:47.42,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It looks like we're gonna keep \NLicht and the others waiting a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:50.50,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Eclat, we're going to do {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:51.78,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:55.20,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:14:59.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.29,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:08.55,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the spell Gauche \Nused to evade attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.43,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.87,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Licht's Demon-Destroyer Sword severs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:19.14,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,the cause-and-effect relationships around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:23.87,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,He has the ability to nullify Eclat's \Neye magic, so I'll get rid of him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.36,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:30.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:33.11,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Can you evade attacks with your eyes closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:36.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can evade using ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:40.08,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in that case... How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:47.17,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That many... This definitely isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:49.92,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:53.53,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it's our turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:57.18,italics,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,...t-t-t-to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:59.18,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:08.07,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna rip right through \Nthat in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:28.00,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.23,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.52,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,...looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:49.40,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The magic item in his left eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.10,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:53.67,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of you, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.51,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wipe out every last speck of you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.47,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,so you can't fight us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:04.96,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't undo the binding spell in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.59,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:09.96,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,M-My magic can't reach that high!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.88,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:21.89,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:26.13,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:29.42,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Poison Magic: Violett Schirm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.75,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.82,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Conversion: Poison to Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.81,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:57.14,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,As we thought... Gauche is way \Nstronger than usual right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.34,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:05.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.42,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:09.65,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I can still figh—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:17.86,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.16,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:24.54,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Of... course... I... am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:32.04,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Magic... please hold out just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.92,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:41.10,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Just like many mages reinforce \Nthemselves by using magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:44.59,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Henry uses his magic to keep himself alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:49.01,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His blood vessels, muscles, and basically \Nall of his organs are very frail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:52.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He cannot stay alive unless he \Ncontinually uses magic to reinforce them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.24,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,What he'd been given was
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.69,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,a constitution that absorbed magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:01.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to absorb \Nmagical powers from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:07.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Despite being born into a renowned \Nnoble family, his body was just too frail,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:12.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and his family... the world could \Nnot accept him for what he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.01,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:18.07,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,If we continue to harbor that creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.55,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,it'll disgrace the great name of Legolant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.29,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But he's our child!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:25.18,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.82,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,This is for our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.93,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It was the warped love of high society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.27,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing Henry's parents gave him
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.19,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,was a house in the forest that stored up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:38.99,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,magic power while remaining \Nunseen by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:41.86,Flashback_Italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:45.45,Flashback_Italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I just cause everyone trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.75,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the resident ghost that \Neveryone keeps talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:54.25,flashback,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm... not... \Nactually... a... ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:57.11,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, I'm Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:01.05,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I just became a Magic Knights\NSquad captain recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.55,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm looking for a hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:06.97,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Up until that moment, I was basically dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.10,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.81,flashback,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,But... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:17.57,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, you just need a lively bunch \Nof people to live here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:23.97,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,My house became the hideout of the \NBlack Bulls, and up until that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.85,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:34.46,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I have my \Nlife now is because of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:37.69,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't care what happens to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.68,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to get through Eclat's binding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.80,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna stop you two, no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:54.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and turn you back into the \Nnormal Gauche and Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:01.19,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm going to save him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:03.84,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.94,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save my friend!
