Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:41.73,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:46.01,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}You Saw
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:44.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You Saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:48.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna stop you two, no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.85,0:22:51.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and turn you back into the \Nnormal Gauche and Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.97,0:22:53.62,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Droit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:22:56.06,main,Eclat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Eclat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:22:58.18,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,We're never turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:23:02.56,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But... I do want to know a little \Nmore about this human named Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:07.73,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This doll that looks just like Eclat \Nthat I had when I reincarnated...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.71,0:23:10.07,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It's just too cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:14.99,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And these pictures of her \Nin different outfits...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:17.95,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,He's got such good taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.89,0:23:20.49,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This guy knows what he's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:22.00,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:24.71,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:29.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Marie's doll and pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:31.72,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:33.47,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.67,0:23:36.31,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:41.89,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Next... time... on... {\i1}Black... Clover,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.22,0:23:47.31,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Page... 112: "Humans Who Can Be Trusted."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:54.03,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 111\N\N{\fs18}Humans Who Can Be Trusted
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.31,0:23:53.87,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,It's... my... job... to... \Nsave... my... friends.
